{"key":"content:1.getting-started:4.commands.md","generatedAt":"2021-10-13T13:08:12.857Z","mtime":"2021-10-13T13:08:12.848Z","slug":"commands","title":"命令","position":"000100040000","to":"/getting-started/commands","draft":false,"page":true,"language":"en","empty":false,"description":"Nuxi是适用于Nuxt 3的一个新的命令行界面。","body":{"raw":"<!--\n * @Author: web.王晓冬\n * @Date: 2021-10-12 22:48:05\n * @LastEditors: web.王晓冬\n * @LastEditTime: 2021-10-13 20:15:37\n * @Description: file content\n-->\n# 命令\n\nNuxi是适用于Nuxt 3的一个新的命令行界面。\n\nNuxt 3有两个主要命令，一个是启动开发服务器，一个是制作production assets。\n\n，，自从Since  becomes a dev dependency thanks to the new由于新的 [Nitro server](/concepts/server-engine), Nuxt 3成为一个开发依赖。自此，你只需要在你的 `package.json`中添加两个命令:\n\n```json\n\"scripts\": {\n  \"dev\": \"nuxi dev\",\n  \"build\": \"nuxi build\",\n}\n```\n\n然后使用 `npm run <command>` 或 `yarn <command>`运行每个命令。\n\n## 开发服务器\n\n在http://localhost:3000: 上使用模块热替换来启动开发模式下的Nuxt:\n\n::code-group\n```bash[Yarn]\nyarn dev\n```\n```bash[NPM]\nnpm run dev\n```\n::\n\n## Building for production\n\n创建应用程序并运行：\n\n::code-group\n```bash[Yarn]\nyarn build\n```\n```bash[NPM]\nnpm run build\n```\n::\n\nNuxt将会为你即将部署的应用程序，服务器和依赖创建一个[`.output`](/docs/directory-structure/output) 目录。 请查看[deployment](/docs/deployment) 了解在何处以及如何使用Nitro部署一个Nuxt应用程序。","ast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"prose-h1","props":{"class":"d-heading-title","id":"命令"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"命令"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"prose-paragraph","props":{"class":"d-heading-description"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Nuxi是适用于Nuxt 3的一个新的命令行界面。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"prose-paragraph","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Nuxt 3有两个主要命令，一个是启动开发服务器，一个是制作production assets。"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"prose-paragraph","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"，，自从Since  becomes a dev dependency thanks to the new由于新的